snippet.title: Horror Plant 2
snippet.description: Horror Plant 2 Puzzle game. Try to get the plant as big as possible eating all human beings each of the levels.

snippet.title: Magi: The Fallen World
snippet.description: Magi: The Fallen World RPG adventure. Pick a character and look for quests, explore dungeons and fight powerful monsters.

snippet.title: Effing Worms 2
snippet.description: Effing Worms 2 Action game. You are a very hungry worm and you feed on the living creature of this planet!

snippet.title: Infectonator 2
snippet.description: Infectonator 2 Strategy game. Raise a zombie army and try to infect all people in the world with the zombie virus.

snippet.title: Transmorpher
snippet.description: Transmorpher Platform adventure. Reach the exit of each stage using the special morphing powers you have.

snippet.title: The Suspense 2
snippet.description: The Suspense 2 Platform adventure. Travel through time to prevent yourself from getting killed as fast as you can.

snippet.title: Pheus And Mor
snippet.description: Pheus And Mor Platform puzzle. Help Pheus and Mor to get to the exit of each level controlling them both to succeed.

snippet.title: Corporate Wars: Lost Levels
snippet.description: Corporate Wars: Lost Levels Tower defense game. Defend your base by building towers along the path to attack enemy units.

snippet.title: Sparkman: Stop World
snippet.description: Sparkman: Stop World Platform game. Try to collect all the dots in order to activate the exitpoint of each level.

snippet.title: Resort Empire
snippet.description: Resort Empire Management game. Build your dream resort from scratch and become the best in the world.
